  "notes": "Different alignment for Man and Lady on steps 3-4. Man is doing swiveling through his feet. Lady changes from PP to Man's L side and then R side, OP. Do not drop R side, ribs to Man. Man is doing swiveling through his feet. Lady changes from PP to Man's L side and then R side, OP. Use glute, pick up the hip fwd, Swing hip fwd and up. Take head to L and keep head head through the rest of steps. Do not try making connection by arching the back. Have loose contact with Man, sliding from one side to another. Use L glute to push. Swing R hip. Feather finish. Different alignment for Man and Lady on steps 3-4. Q: RF to side | Backing Wall | TH | 1/8 between 3-4, body turns less | Sway(L) | Up. Use L glute to push. Swing R hip. Feather finish. Q: LF back in CBMP | Backing DW | TH | - | Sway(L) | Up. Lower e/o 5",
